---
import GreenDot from "../images/background-shape/green-dot.webp";
import BlueDot from "../images/background-shape/blue-dot.webp";
import HalfCircle from "../images/background-shape/green-half-cycle.webp";
import SeoBall from "../images/background-shape/seo-ball-1.webp";
import TeamBgTriangle from "../images/background-shape/team-bg-triangle.webp";
import ServiceHalfCycle from "../images/background-shape/service-half-cycle.webp";
---

<section id="about" class="section p-auto-width-responsive fp-auto-height-responsive section-lg about pb-0" data-anchor="about-anchor">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row max-ch-row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">About us</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-12 mb-100">
            <p>
            Siamo <strong>Kristian Buriasco</strong> e <strong>Lorenzo Marchisio</strong>, due studenti delle scuole superiori con una passione per lo <strong>sviluppo web</strong>. Insieme, portiamo le nostre <strong>competenze tecniche</strong>, <strong>attenzione ai dettagli</strong> e <strong>soluzioni innovative</strong> a ogni progetto su cui lavoriamo. Il nostro sito web presenta il nostro <strong>portfolio di progetti</strong> passati e il nostro impegno nel fornire <strong>esperienze utente eccezionali</strong>. Siamo sempre aggiornati con le <strong>ultime tendenze del settore</strong> e dedicati a aiutare i nostri clienti a raggiungere il <strong>successo online</strong>. Dalla <strong>concezione</strong> all'<strong>uscita</strong>, lavoreremo a <strong>stretto contatto</strong> con te per comprendere le tue <strong>esigenze uniche</strong> e far prendere vita alla tua <strong>visione</strong>. Aiutaci a stabilire o migliorare la tua <strong>presenza online</strong> con un <strong>sito web stupefacente</strong>.
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- background shapes -->
    <img
        src={GreenDot}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-1 up-down-animation"
    />
    <img
        src={BlueDot}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-2 left-right-animation"
    />
    <img
        src={HalfCircle}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-3 up-down-animation"
    />
    <img
        src={SeoBall}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-4 left-right-animation"
    />
    <img
        src={TeamBgTriangle}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-5 up-down-animation"
    />
    <img
        src={ServiceHalfCycle}
        alt="background-shape"
        class="about-bg-6 left-right-animation"
    />
</section>



<style lang="scss">
@import "../styles/variables.scss";

.about {
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
    &-video {
        position: relative;
        .play-btn {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
    }
    
    &-bg-1{
        position: absolute;
        left: 30%;
        top: 10%;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    &-bg-2{
        position: absolute;
        top: 30%;
        right: 40px;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    &-bg-3{
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 20%;
        left: 30px;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    &-bg-4{
        position: absolute;
        top: 20%;
        left: 40px;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    &-bg-5{
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 10%;
        right: 40px;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    &-bg-6{
        position: absolute;
        top: 10%;
        right: 10%;
        z-index: -1;
        @include tablet {
            display: none;
        }
    }

    .max-ch-row {
        max-width: 70ch;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }
}


.play-btn {
    height: 70px;
    width: 70px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: $white;
    line-height: 70px;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #7aff91;
